= Limelight Changelog

== Version 0.3.0

Major New Release
* Many new feature and much more stability
* Default event implementation - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/52)
* Image player - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/63)
* Sending variables to partials - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/61)
* CPU Hog -  (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/35)
* Gems in productions - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/12)
* Giving Floats to prop styles - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/17)
* Scene's Default name - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/47)
* Hand Cursor Stays - bug (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/36)
* generate production templates - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/46)
* Validate styles - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/53)
* Auto resizing doesn't trigger update on parent. - bug (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/51)
* Double click to open production - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/27)
* Color as a hash - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/32)
* Add more Known colors - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/54)
* Need to relaunch when changing player. - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/50)
* Shared Players - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/48)
* Unique IDs - bug (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/49)
* Building a Production - documentation (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/41)
* Document Events - documentation (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/15)
* Document Prop API - documentation (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/16)
* Document Styles - documentation (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/14)
* Variable size text areas - feature_request (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/37)
* Editable TextArea size - bug (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/39)
* Simple App screencast - documentation (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/42)
* RDoc - documentation (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/40)
* finish 0.2.0 release - release (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/43)
* Reserved prop keywords - bug (http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/45)

== Version 0.2.1

Minor Fixes
* stripped DSL builder of all methods except those needed.
* catch uneeded paint updates
* text measurement fixed
* frame insets detectable and used in sizing
* rdoc

== Version 0.2.0

Redesigned Model
* The UI model was redesigned to avoid such of Swing's hierarchy
* Changes listed here: http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073-limelight/tickets?q=milestone%3A%22Limelight+0.2%22&filter=all

